1.5
log
@Discard excess head arguments for .Bd .Bl .Bk and delete hwarn_eq0().
Discard empty .Bk blocks.
Improve related diagnostics.
@
text
@.Dd June 30, 2010
.Dt BK-BADARG 1
.Os OpenBSD
.Sh NAME
.Nm Bk-badarg
.Nd bad arguments after Bk
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Ar x x x x x x x x
.Ar x x x x x x x x
.Ar x x x x x x x x
.Ar x x x x x x
.Bk -badarg
.Op o Ar a
.Ek
.Pp
.Nm
.Ar x x x x x x x x
.Ar x x x x x x x x
.Ar x x x x x x x x
.Ar x x x x x x
.Bk -lines
.Op o Ar a
.Ek tail argument
.Pp
.Nm
.Ar x x x x x x x x
.Ar x x x x x x x x
.Ar x x x x x x x x
.Ar x x x x x x
.Bk -line
.Op o Ar a
.Ek
.Pp
.Nm
.Ar x x x x x x x x
.Ar x x x x x x x x
.Ar x x x x x x x x
.Ar x x x x x x
.Bk
.Op o Ar a
.Ek
.Pp
.Nm
.Ar x x x x x x x x
.Ar x x x x x x x x
.Ar x x x x x x x x
.Ar x x x x x x
.Bk -words -murks bogus
.Op o Ar a
.Ek
.Sh DESCRIPTION
Here is an empty keep:
.Bk -words
.Ek
End of test document.
@


1.4
